            "transform": "param_to_var",
            "description": "Route ERA5 grid longitude to EDGARv81MonthlyEmis lon parameter. param_to_var replaces the EDGAR.lon default (0.0 rad) with the runtime ERA5.lon value. Units: rad (both sides). Source: EarthSciData.jl@830435a src/coupling.jl:31 (_couple_emis_to_met)."
        },
